Subject: [PATCH] drm/amdgpu: Reset IH OVERFLOW_CLEAR bit

[ Upstream commit 7330256268664ea0a7dd5b07a3fed363093477dd ]

Allows us to detect subsequent IH ring buffer overflows as well.

